    {
      "id": "26.8.1_heading",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.8.1",
      "text": "26.8.1 Wind Speed-Up over Hills, Ridges, and Escarpments",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "left",
      "heading": true,
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.8.1_provision",
      "type": "provision",
      "section": "26.8.1",
      "text": "Wind speed-up effects at isolated hills, ridges, and escarpments constituting abrupt changes in the general topography, located in any exposure category, shall be included in the determination of the wind loads when site conditions and locations of buildings and other structures meet all the following conditions:",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "left",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.8.1_conditions",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.8.1",
      "text": "1. The building or other structure is located as shown in Figure 26.8-1 in the upper one-half of a hill or ridge or near the crest of an escarpment.\n2. H/Lh ≥ 0.2.\n3. H is greater than or equal to 15 ft (4.5 m) for Exposures C and D and 60 ft (18 m) for Exposures B.",
      "cross_references": [
        "Figure 26.8-1"
      ],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "left",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.8.2_heading",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.8.2",
      "text": "26.8.2 Topographic Factor",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "right",
      "heading": true,
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.8.2_provision",
      "type": "provision",
      "section": "26.8.2",
      "text": "The wind speed-up effect shall be included in the calculation of design wind loads by using the factor Kzt:",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "right",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.8.2_formula",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.8.2",
      "text": "Kzt = (1 + K1K2K3)²",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "right",
      "expression": "Kzt = (1 + K1K2K3)²",
      "parameters": [
        "[object Object]",
        "[object Object]",
        "[object Object]",
        "[object Object]"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.8.2_k_factors",
      "type": "provision",
      "section": "26.8.2",
      "text": "where K1, K2, and K3 are given in Figure 26.8-1. The values for K2 and K3 shall not be less than 0. The equations for K1, K2, and K3 may be used instead of using the tabular values when increased accuracy is desired for evaluating K1 and substitute 2H for Lh for evaluating K2 and K3.",
      "cross_references": [
        "Figure 26.8-1"
      ],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "right",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.8.2_site_conditions",
      "type": "provision",
      "section": "26.8.2",
      "text": "If site conditions and locations of buildings and other structures do not meet all the conditions specified in Section 26.8.1, then Kzt = 1.0.",
      "cross_references": [
        "Section 26.8.1"
      ],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "right",
      "metadata": {
