    {
      "id": "26.10.1_provision",
      "type": "provision",
      "section": "26.10.1",
      "text": "Based on the exposure category determined in Section 26.7.3, a velocity pressure exposure coefficient, Kz or Kh, as applicable, shall be determined from Table 26.10-1. For a site located in a transition zone between exposure categories that is near to a change in ground surface roughness, intermediate values of Kz or Kh between those shown in Table 26.10-1 are permitted provided they are determined by a rational analysis method defined in the recognized literature.",
